oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry Welcomes Trace Adkins (5th Opry Anniversary)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Adkins, Trace; Grand ole opry (Radio program); Metal photoplates; restrikes;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black, yellow, and red on white) announcing the Grand Ole Opry's newest member Trace Adkins inducted on August 23, 2003. Poster features a metal photoplate of Trace Adkins and was reprinted for the Fifth Opry Anniversary of Trace Adkins' induction.
